Classified Skins.name: AK-47 | Jet Set
Classified Skins.desc: Its stock has been wrapped in brown leather. This weapon has been to a lot of cities.
Classified Skins.lore: Anyone paying close attention will connect the dots and see what she did. We don't have much time to find a solution... - A Father's Love Part 1

Restricted Skins.name: AK-47 | First Class
Restricted Skins.desc: Its stock has been wrapped in green leather.

Restricted Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Pilot

Mil-Spec Skins.name: XM1014 | Red Leather

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Pack your baags. Let's go kill that sonofabitch... - The Oni and The Valkyrie Part 2

Consumer Grade Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Green Plaid
